data.description: List all the style options available. Also list the "styleKey" which needs to be passed onto image or video endpoint to specify the kind of style to be applied. The response contains canonical title and the original style image.

data.name: Image
content_file
data.description: Original Image to be convert into art form

data.name: scale_height
data.description: Height of the resultant image (aspect ratio is maintained). Either pass scale_width or scale_height.

data.name: scale_width
data.description: Width of the resultant image (aspect ratio is maintained). Either pass scale_width or scale_height.

data.name: style
data.description: Style which needs to be applied on the original image. Options available are starry_night, composition, seurat, candy, edtaonisl, cubist_style, fur, hokusai, kanagawa, kandinsky and many more options available.
Process video files. Limited to 10 seconds and 10 FPS. For better quality contact administrator. Please drop us a mail at hey@neuralpainting.co before you use the API in production.
data.name: Video
scale_height

data.name: scale_width
data.description: Width of the resultant video (aspect ratio is maintained). Either pass scale_width or scale_height.

data.name: style

description:
Convert videos and images into neural art in realtime.
NeuralPainting is an HTTP REST API to convert image and videos into neural art, out-of-the-box.
